{"tid":373613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【太子有難】韓三星集團掌舵人李在鎔 行賄罪成判監5年","createTime":"2017-08-25T06:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T08:31:32.000Z","uid":47272,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d87c7a06bdf3581007c375fa10bdfeb1f332b48","tid":373613,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:39:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170825&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57124926\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170825%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57124926&d=O6BCfiSzhlV6ZlY4K8ylW54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=4a57ef23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170825%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57124926&h=42b5dce9\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170825&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57124926</a><br />\n南韓三星集團掌舵人李在鎔涉嫌行賄案宣判，首爾中央地區法院一審判處他行賄及其他罪名全部成立。<br />\n<br />\n法官指李在鎔為有利自己在三星集團的接班工作，賄賂前總統朴槿惠，又牽涉挪用64億韓圜（約4,500萬港元），而且有作偽證行為，以及有份資助朴槿惠親信崔順實的女兒鄭尤拉接受馬術訓練。<br />\n<br />\n現年49歲的李在鎔是三星集團會長李健熙獨子，亦是三星電子副會長，2014年成為集團實際掌舵人。他被指向前總統朴槿惠及其親信崔順實行賄約433億韓圜（約3億港元），以換取青瓦台支持三星2間子公司合併，進一步鞏固權力。檢方起訴李在鎔行賄、舞弊、挪用公款、隱瞞海外資產及偽證等罪名，並求刑12年。<br />\n<br />\n自李在鎔2月被扣查後，消息指旗艦子公司三星電子召開的策略會議減少，重要決策滯後。而知情人士指，三星集團作為全球最大手機生產商集團，內部並未就李在鎔一旦入獄制訂應變計劃，意味今日過後三星或長期陷於群龍無首的窘局。<br />\n<br />\n而已被罷黜的前總統朴槿惠和崔順實，亦分別因「親信門」被拘控，如今李在鎔被定罪，兩人應難撇清指控。朴槿惠受賄案預計在9月宣判。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社/路透社/美聯社/《蘋果》資料室"},{"pid":"0b8ba91c34b43181f3cb3b792097f232ce39009b","tid":373613,"uid":91152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:41:41.000Z","msg":"連登冇人會理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3a46907eb4ab48d136c3de3ce685233b9600d5","tid":373613,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q1si28n3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq1si28n3&h=59b88d9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08482ecf58620b04273478b23712ca177dc79060","tid":373613,"uid":107231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:48:29.000Z","msg":"又唔係抄家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e932d1bce16e385732d2c4bfce5ef416a82edba","tid":373613,"uid":91152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:52:30.000Z","msg":"Yet he may yet escape a jail term even if he is convicted. Many top executives of South Korea's biggest companies, including his father, have been convicted of crimes but were pardoned.<br />\n<br />\nSource: BBC"},{"pid":"b8cff1bfc6700561c1c08d060472369a9b9d2e1a","tid":373613,"uid":36738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:31:39.000Z","msg":"樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d811c1761d4e930ea4ff29c75dda59da15a6d00","tid":373613,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:49:31.000Z","msg":"到時又特赦"},{"pid":"547f50f38b1e9c99b7efd5b1796ed8c3c646d9d3","tid":373613,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T08:21:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到時又特赦</blockquote><br />\n好難講<br />\n新總統上台無耐，特赦有損威信"},{"pid":"e98662ba38128aa575beef6822414ce962c95b57","tid":373613,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T08:28:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d344432e8c30ff349eb2964f8fb63aa69c2c15b0","tid":373613,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T08:29:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話三星共和國個個唔敢得罪佢</blockquote><br />\n呢次高層權力鬥爭，連女總統都賴嘢，何況一個商人。"},{"pid":"acb47ca41a6060f4ef178f8f8530a9abffc44859","tid":373613,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T08:31:32.000Z","msg":"WFC, 有S8用就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}